Package: scoringrules
Type: Package
Title: Scoring Rules for Evaluating Probabilistic Forecasts
Version: 1.0
Date: 2014-09-11
Author: Alexander Jordan, Fabian Krueger, Sebastian Lerch
Maintainer: Fabian Krueger <Fabian.Krueger83@gmail.com>
Description: Functions to evaluate probabilistic forecasts, with an 
	emphasis on forecasts that come in the form of a simulated sample (as in MCMC).
License: GPL (>= 2.0)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.2)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
